          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HE greatest Monarch may be stabb'd by Night,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-2" n="2">And Fortune help the Murd'rer in his Flight;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-3" n="3">The vilest Ruffian may commit a Rape,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-4" n="4">Yet safe from injured Innocence escape;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-5" n="5">And Calumny, by working under Ground,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-6" n="6">Can, unreveng'd, the greatest Merit wound.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-7" n="7"><lb/>W<hi rend="small-caps">HAT</hi>'s to be done? shall Wit and Learning chuse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-8" n="8">To live obscure, and have no Fame to lose?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-9" n="9">By Censure frighted out of Honour's Road,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-10" n="10">Nor dare to use the Gifts by Heav'n bestow'd;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-11" n="11">Or fearless enter in thro' Virtue's Gate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-58D3-line-12" n="12">And buy Distinction at the dearest Rate.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
